ibis.cashmere.constellation

Class LibFuncLaunch

  • java.lang.Object
    • ibis.cashmere.constellation.Launch
      • ibis.cashmere.constellation.LibFuncLaunch

  • public class LibFuncLaunch
extends Launch
    Represents one specific launch of a LibFunc. While launch(ibis.cashmere.constellation.LaunchFunction) methods can only be called once, it is possible to create multiple launches from a LibFunc.
